American Assets Investment Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:42 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of American Assets Investment Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
American Asset Investment Management LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also provides its services to pension and profit sharing plans, and corporations. The firm also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in public equity and fixed income market of United States. The firm also invests in real estates. It obtains externals research to complement its in-house research. American Asset Investment Management LLC was founded in 2002 and is based in San Diego, California.


